item.title: 2020-02-26 07:30 Agila Halmstad Breakfast: Back to Being Human
item.description: Welcome to the first breakfast meetup for this new community - Agila Halmstad. We will explore Agile Leadership - in particular we will have a group exercise where the aim is to bring to the surface why this is needed, and what it looks and feels like to "be agile"....
